{"tid":1847452,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Super Junior為武漢肺炎「取消粉絲來看回歸」","createTime":"2020-01-28T05:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T06:00:41.000Z","uid":74065,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c836da8f5316080dfac65af1213d98984e5831bd","tid":1847452,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:17:11.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎持續延燒至世界各地，鄰近國家像是南韓已經有確診4例，知名天團Super Junior將在28日回歸舉辦《COMEBACK SHOW》，前一天就透過官方聲明宣佈因疫情狀況取消讓粉絲入場參與錄影。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4671/d4671360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4671%2Fd4671360.jpg&h=798b0f79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Super Junior即將回歸但碰上武漢肺炎。（圖／翻攝自Super Junior臉書）<br />\n<br />\nSuper Junior於27日對外宣布：「由於近期的新型冠狀病毒（武漢肺炎）相關事項，原本預定1月28日進行的Super Junior表演等全部錄影將更改為非公開形式，由於事前準備的關係要變更日期有一定的困難度，不得已的狀況下轉為非公開形式錄影，希望有申請的粉絲能夠諒解，當日預計進行的VLIVE直播不會變動，未來也請多多關注Super Junior表演。」<br />\n<br />\n韓網看了都稱讚Super Junior方的判斷相當正確，「取消是對的，雖然粉絲會覺得很可惜」、「做得好！要是等真的有事情發生再來處理都來不及了」、「這是很正確的對策決定，在封閉空間有400個人尖叫應援（有2次總共800人），這些人之中中國、香港和台灣等都是確診案例地區的粉絲占大多數，這樣就成了感染的最佳環境，要是粉絲出現感染者就都會怪藝人，因此我認為是很聰明的決定」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4671/e4671367.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4671%2Fe4671367.jpg&h=cab5dd88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4671/e4671368.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4671%2Fe4671368.jpg&h=1395cf24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲韓網回應。（圖／翻攝自THEQOO、NATE新聞）"},{"pid":"36bfb74b68e12dfad0623964dc5d91f40f5cf1b5","tid":1847452,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T06:00:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我同醫護一齊罷工</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.29抗疫三罷X黎明行動<br />\n每日消毒手機眼鏡</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E6yiTok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE6yiTok.jpg&h=1be6d8c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w7DKFeP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw7DKFeP.jpg&h=b66c14c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fegggw0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffegggw0.jpg&h=356cfd5e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xRLkX1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxRLkX1F.jpg&h=dfb9a9db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">醫管局員工罷工陣線</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cz3Oj3C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcz3Oj3C.jpg&h=75c5a0f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MRMzZ3D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMRMzZ3D.jpg&h=6c372ba0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}